    <p>
      What’s the best way to get to know people at uni? How do you remember what you learn in lectures?
      Why should you always be true to yourself? There’s only one way to find out.
      Dig into our top university hacks from our recently qualified teachers.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-845">
    <%= render Content::PhotoQuoteListComponent.new(
      [
        {
          image: "static/images/content/food-for-thought/Amrita_Panesar.jpg",
          heading: "Find support",
          text: "I used the student support networks to find help and support, and they offered mental health support and help with assignments and coursework when needed. I also spoke to students in years above to get some advice about my course.",
